data.description: Need a house with everything? This is the one! Beautifully remodeled kitchen, newer flooring throughout and tons of storage! Gourmet kitchen features upgrades including granite counters, gas stove, super quiet dishwasher, undermount granite sink and beautiful cabinetry to the ceiling! Master bedroom has en suite with dual vanities, soaker tub, walk in shower and huge closet.  Fully fenced backyard has 12 x14 gazebo, 14x16 shed, 35' RV pad with 30amp plug in and space for gardening! Located in a quiet neighborhood tucked away from the main road. Save money each month on electricity with SOLAR panels and avoid storage fees with the RV parking on your own property!!
